components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        errorId: {type: string}
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        errorId: {type: string}
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth: {scheme: basic, type: http}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of McAfee Network Security Manger
  title: McAfee Network Security Manger
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Quarantine Host in Network Security Manager
      parameters:
      - description: Quarantine host on this sensor.
        example: '1001'
        in: query
        name: Sensor ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: IP Address to quarantine
        example: 102.012.102.102
        in: query
        name: IP Address
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Duration in quarantine. Can be 'FIFTEEN_MINUTES', 'THIRTY_MINUTES',
          'FORTYFIVE_MINUTES', 'SIXTY_MINUTES','FOUR_HOURS', 'EIGHT_HOURS','TWELVE_HOURS','SIXTEEN_HOURS','UNTIL_EXPLICITLY_RELEASED'.  Default
          is UNTIL_EXPLICITLY_RELEASED.
        example: SIXTEEN_HOURS
        in: query
        name: Duration
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Remediate the IP along with quarantine
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Remediate
        required: true
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Quarantine Host
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Release quarantined host from Network Security Manager
      parameters:
      - description: Release quarantined host on this sensor.
        example: '1001'
        in: query
        name: Sensor ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: IP Address to release
        example: 102.012.102.102
        in: query
        name: IP Address
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Release Quarantined Host
tags:
- {name: Network Security & Management}
